ActFood and Drugs Act
Controlled Drugs and Substances Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Department of Health Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) correct references to section numbering; (2) correct a discrepancy between the French and English versions; (3) harmonize terms used in the regulations with those used in the enabling statute; (4) add clarity to a regulatory provision; (5) correct typographical or grammatical errors; and (6) repeal obsolete, spent or redundant regulatory provisions.
